{"word":"G4691 - σπερμολόγος - spermológos - sper-mol-og'-os - Babbler","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπερμολόγος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">spermológos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sper-mol-og'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Babbler</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வாயாடி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"babbler, loafer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4690 - σπέρμα - spérma - sper'-mah/4690\">G4690</a> and <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a>; a <i>seed picker</i> (as the crow), that is, (figuratively) a <i>sponger</i>, <i>loafer</i> (specifically a <i>gossip</i> or <i>trifler</i> in talk): - babbler.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4687/4687\">G4687</a>, <a href=\"#/G4690/4690\">G4690</a>, <a href=\"#/G4691/4691\">G4691</a>, <a href=\"#/G4701/4701\">G4701</a>, <a href=\"#/G4702/4702\">G4702</a>, <a href=\"#/G4703/4703\">G4703</a>"}]}